      "rationale": "Commercial FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical R2022R2) is covered by vendor-supplied IQ/OQ/PQ qualification package accepted under FDA 21 CFR Part 11. Analysis scripts are version-controlled; an independent analyst verified reproducibility across three representative load cases. Achieved Gradation 3 exceeds the required Gradation 2 for a Medium model-risk, Medium decision-consequence COU."
