      },
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical's built-in verification test suite covers linear and nonlinear static structural problems. Benchmark cases for beam-column bending and Hertzian contact — the dominant physics in the F1717 model — were run and passed within documented solver tolerances. Gradation 2 achieved and meets the required level."
