        "description": "Material properties (E=113.8 GPa, σ_y=880 MPa, E_t=1.14 GPa) sourced from ASTM F136 coupon data provided by DePuy Synthes; geometry from certified CAD files with dimensional inspection report; boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture constraints. All inputs documented in technical file with traceability to primary sources."
      },
      "rationale": "All model inputs are traceable to primary sources: material properties from manufacturer-supplied coupon test data (N=5 per batch), geometry from certified CAD with CMM inspection, and boundary conditions directly mapped from ASTM F1717 test fixture drawings. Uncertainty in material properties propagated via ±1σ Monte Carlo (N=500 runs) to bound QoI sensitivity. Gradation 3 achieved."
