        "name": "Test samples acceptance criteria",
        "description": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories (FDA OSEL and DePuy Synthes internal); samples drawn from same production lot as CAD geometry; dimensional inspection confirms geometry within ±0.05 mm of nominal."
      },
      "rationale": "Eleven constructs tested across two independent laboratories provide inter-laboratory reproducibility data. All samples are from the same certified production lot whose geometry was used to build the FEA model, ensuring material-geometric consistency. Dimensional inspection confirmed all critical features within ±0.05 mm of nominal CAD. Gradation 3 exceeds required Gradation 2."
