      },
      "rationale": "The three QoIs — construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement — are identical to those specified in ASTM F1717 and used in the regulatory submission for substantial equivalence. No surrogate quantities were substituted. These QoIs directly characterize the failure modes relevant to the COU (construct fracture under spinal compression-bending loads). Gradation 3 achieved."
